rComments: Very clear & interesting. One of the less academic & more pedagogue profs. Truly interesting classes. Do your reading and listen to him & you'll get a really good grade. However he does sometimes look & speaks like he just got out of a coma and he did all his suit shopping in the 80s-90s so he looks kinda funny at times.

This prof is amazing! He doesn't speak very fast so at first you might think uh-oh this will be a long semester, but at the end of the 3 hour classes, I didn't want it to stop! He delivers the information clearly, and his exams are VERY easy (if you read the book).
This dude rocks. Knows the material inside out and makes it interesting to be in class. You have to love his senate stories.. Def. Recommended
